Module com.example.gymmembershipgui
Package com.example.gymmembershipgui

Class FitnessClass

java.lang.Object
com.example.gymmembershipgui.FitnessClass
public class FitnessClass extends Object
FitnessClass is defined by attendees, instructor, name, time, and location. For each fitness class, members and guests can be checked-in through the class's database. Members and guests can also be dropped from the class. Additionally, if either member or guest needs to be found in the class, they can be searched for through the participants and guests.
Author:
Mahfuza Rahman, Arunima Tripathy
